IN RE RAYMOND L. FRICK TRUST. Edward M. Kress and Jenny Frick Trychel, also known as Jeni Frick Trychel, Successor Co-Trustees, Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
Bradley Spice and BCL 75, Inc., Defendants-Appellants. SC: 158984
COA: 341498 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 1, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motions for the temporary admission of out-of-state attorneys Susan D. Solle and Thomas P. Whalley, II, to appear and practice in this case under MCR 8.126(A) are GRANTED.
